<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-34-1333 </DOCNO><TEXT>Selected activities of the Metallurgy Department at Risoe National Laboratoryduring 1987 are described. The work is presented in four chapters: MaterialsScience, Materials Engineering, Materials Technology and Energy Programmes.A survey is given of the Department's participation in internationalcollaboration and of its activities within education and training. Furthermore,the main numbers illustrating the Departments's economy are given. Listsof staff members, visiting scientists, publications, lectures and posterpresentations are included. 38 ills.</TEXT></DOC>